cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel anomaly detection approach based on coverage-guided analysis of neural networks. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach also involves analyzing hidden activation values in neural networks, which is related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural engineering (cs.NE). Finally, the paper evaluates the approach on common baseline datasets, which involves analyzing cybersecurity (cs.CR) data.
